name: COVID19ICD10CMValueSetForJuvenileIdiopathicArthritis
title: COVID19 ICD10CM Value Set for Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to juvenile idiopathic arthritis and is listed as a rheumatologic/autoimmune/inflammatory condition on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes juvenile idiopathic arthritis and juvenile rheumatoid arthritis.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes acute juvenile rheumatoid arthritis.)
